{"tid":1534511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好耐冇搭黨鐵，依家平日多唔多人跳閘？","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:39.000Z","uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d74aca4dcd41816edfa45c9911ebe8c24f0a8d60","tid":1534511,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f2592b6504e0a9b83cae33f8bdcf5fe6d58bf9","tid":1534511,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:30:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ae7e39e4b494a9da52aed79d12fe9562ff8a308","tid":1534511,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"儘量唔搭，一搭就跳"},{"pid":"db4a11385ad1427c26b28e32732d88371e75f075","tid":1534511,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:39.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"120611ebfb7c0d0a5029b6740242a63a99457cd0","tid":1534511,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae7e39e4b494a9da52aed79d12fe9562ff8a308","tid":1534511,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"儘量唔搭，一搭就跳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"多唔多人跳？"},{"pid":"fe9ffd8b24d3711b69fa1c98a7196d1d80a0c8f8","tid":1534511,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"me"},{"pid":"c260d58a8c1eec3b20ff41bba29523fdf1995009","tid":1534511,"uid":127543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"其實新式閘一頂就開到"},{"pid":"277b1cfcfa8cc58a405d79bd59868226ce84e4ed","tid":1534511,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"教你用經濟學角度去長期抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534263\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534263</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"abaffdc47e0d42ef9233ae8e77c12d21bd324c95","tid":1534511,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"215329a3e41fb5a98272e3b22fd25c66f49323dd","tid":1534511,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:11.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFKooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=91927e61\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"9de953c0720794a91536b79d9849b12335d98c9e","tid":1534511,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:39:35.000Z","msg":"日撚日都跳啊，同我跳佢老未黨鐵"},{"pid":"4e6e68ec6841d26bab9f2ff55165853d221d2aed","tid":1534511,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"[法律] [一石二鳥] 教你點攞法庭命令迫黨鐵交太子站CCTV 再告埋香港警察同港鐵！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534194</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">有冇人識831太子車廂嘅人 佢哋出嚟先可以拎CCTV 睇下有冇人死</span></strong><br />\n</span><br />\n個撚個話關心義士 去太子送花<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nFOWARD去各大tg group/tg channel問下有冇人識當日太子站手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋遲一秒佢哋就del多秒"},{"pid":"bc08d386328e4b2704421bb0baea9027ead9624c","tid":1534511,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"120611ebfb7c0d0a5029b6740242a63a99457cd0","tid":1534511,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae7e39e4b494a9da52aed79d12fe9562ff8a308","tid":1534511,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"儘量唔搭，一搭就跳"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"多唔多人跳？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"暫時未目擊過其他人跳"}]}